"打开 CLI 会启动应用生成的 Claude Code patched runtime；当前账号是 Codex 时，即使环境显示为 Claude 凭据模式，也会直接复用该账号当前的 Codex OAuth 或 API Key 启动，不要求 Claude 登录，也不需要额外填写 Base URL 或 API Key。" = "Launching the CLI uses the app-managed patched Claude Code runtime. When the current account is Codex, even if the environment is shown as Claude credentials mode, the app directly reuses the current Codex OAuth or API key. No Claude login, Base URL, or API key entry is required.";
"打开 CLI 会启动应用生成的 Claude Code patched runtime；当前账号是 Codex 时，会默认继承该账号的 Codex 环境启动。若来源环境本身使用当前账号凭据，会直接复用当前 Codex OAuth 或 API Key，不要求 Claude 登录，也不需要手动填写 Base URL 或 API Key。" = "Launching the CLI uses the app-managed patched Claude Code runtime. When the current account is Codex, the app inherits that account's Codex environment by default. If the source environment uses account credentials, it directly reuses the current Codex OAuth or API key. No Claude login or manual Base URL / API key entry is required.";
"当此环境用于 Codex 账号时，应用会自动继承当前账号的 Codex 环境启动 Claude Code，并直接复用当前 Codex OAuth 或 API Key；切到 Claude 账号时，才会沿用 Claude 账号凭据或 Anthropic API Key。" = "When this environment is used with a Codex account, the app automatically inherits the current account's Codex environment to launch Claude Code and directly reuses the current Codex OAuth or API key. When used with a Claude account, it falls back to Claude account credentials or an Anthropic API key.";
"此模式不会要求 Claude 登录；当前账号是 Codex 时，会默认自动继承该账号的 Codex 环境。若来源环境本身使用当前账号凭据，会直接复用当前 Codex OAuth 或 API Key；你也可以手动指定一个覆盖来源环境。" = "This mode does not require Claude login. When the current account is Codex, it automatically inherits that account's Codex environment. If the source environment uses account credentials, it directly reuses the current Codex OAuth or API key. You can still choose an override source environment manually.";
